                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-66-defend666 t18060219-66-punish369"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
